                <aside id="idealab-improvement">
                    <h2>Improve this idea</h2>
                    <p>The Beautiful Solutions Gallery is a collaborative work-in-progress that will continue to grow over the coming months. We will publish new entries based on your ideas, and improve and expand upon existing ones.</p>
                    <p>Please help us improve existing entries by sharing examples of the idea in action, resources that explore the idea, and questions that help to clarify the ideaâ€™s usefulness. Keeping your suggestions short and specific will make it easier for us to incorporate your feedback. Thanks in advance for helping make this toolbox as beautiful as it can be!</p>
                    <button type="button" class="add-an-example">Add an example</button>
